title: DCP ARCHIVE EDITIONS - IRON MAN (1987-2008) (Kritter-DCP)
description:
I found these when looking for all the issues of Iron Man 2.0 to fill a request. Thought they'd make a good torrent.

19 compilations put together by Kritter-DCP, featuring the Armored Avenger. 

Including:

Armor Wars I
Armor Wars II
Dragon Seed
Crash and Burn
Hands of the Mandarin (IM, War Machine, Force Works x-over)
Revenge of the Mandarin
The Eighth Day (IM, Thor, Spider-Man, Juggernaut x-over)

and a lot more.

Please seed and share.  --STF
